Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OP「HIBANA」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:06.50,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}産み落とされた孤独な世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:10.34,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,240)}誰を信じて生きて行く？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:14.38,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人とは何か　闇とは何か
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.38,0:01:17.30,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}飢えたこの目で睨んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:20.39,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正気と忘我　くり返してる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.39,0:01:25.48,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,360)}奈落の底で呼ぶ声響いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:31.57,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}黄泉の路を漂う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.57,0:01:36.49,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,240)}声にひかり差す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:39.41,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}守りたいもの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:42.78,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,240)}変わらないまま
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.78,0:01:48.33,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}精霊転化　絆を強さに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:54.46,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戦い続けよう　踠きながら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:02:03.76,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}崩れそうでも　両手広げ叫んでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:11.90,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,480)}火花を散らし　宿命を背負って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:06.50,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}诞生于孤独的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:10.34,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,240)}我该信任着谁活下去？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:14.38,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知何为人类  何为暗影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.38,0:01:17.30,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只得瞪圆饥渴的双目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:20.39,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}清醒与忘我  不断重复着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.39,0:01:25.48,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,360)}听见奈落深处的呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:31.57,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}飘荡在黄泉之路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.57,0:01:36.49,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,240)}我的声音映照光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:39.41,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}想要守护之物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:42.78,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,240)}未曾改变过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.78,0:01:48.33,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}精灵转化  化情谊为力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:54.46,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一同奋战下去  只管坚持到底
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:02:03.76,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即便摇摇欲坠  也要振臂高呼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:11.90,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,480)}火花灿烂迸放  身怀宿命前行
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED「夕闇のうた」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.65,0:22:18.07,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}光と影が手を取り駆け巡る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.07,0:22:23.33,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}夜の中で生まれた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:30.87,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}小さな手のひらからこの世界に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:34.04,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}愛を届けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:40.30,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}荒れ果てた空の下に咲く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.93,0:22:47.35,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}一番あかるい花びら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.35,0:22:53.56,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}笑いさざめいて君と行く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:22:59.95,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}時の中を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.49,0:23:03.95,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}祈りのように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.95,0:23:07.49,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}天と土を結ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:12.71,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,960)\blur3}君がうたう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.89,0:23:37.07,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}静かなうた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.65,0:22:18.07,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}光影交织巡回之间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.07,0:22:23.33,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}你降生于夜幕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:30.87,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}小小的手掌向着广大世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:34.04,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}播撒爱的种子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:40.30,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}荒天之下唯独绽放着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.93,0:22:47.35,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}那一轮最明亮的花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.35,0:22:53.56,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}欢声笑语中与你同行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:22:59.95,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}走过时间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.49,0:23:03.95,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}如同心愿一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.95,0:23:07.49,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}天地走向大同
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:12.71,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,960)\blur3}只因你的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.89,0:23:37.07,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}静谧之歌
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
